data.description:
MAJOR PRICE REDUCTION Offer Now!

This Oldham County sale is an opportunity for a buyer looking. 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath brick home. The tall ceilings are awesome and layout w/ a primary suite on the FIRST FLOOR. Hardwood floors grace the entire home's first floor rooms. Upstairs, a private suite offers comfort, seclusion or privacy. The finished basement boasts vibrant tile throughout, there is an entertainment area, multiple rooms for guests, office, exercise room & pet washing station in the full bath. 2-car garage & semi-circular driveway makes multiple vehicles/parking easy. The wide backyard is spacious and lush with natural landscape protection & a sound barrier from I-71, that is hard to see. The sale is AS IS and to settle an estate.
